| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **E1**  | 4 GiB | $- | 6,800 | $- | $- | 500 (600) | 60 MB/second (150 MB/second) | $- |
| **E2**  | 8 GiB | $- | 13,400 | $- | $- | 500 (600) | 60 MB/second (150 MB/second) | $- |
